Portia Doubleday https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portia_Doubleday 0 Portia Ann Doubleday (born June 22, 1988) is an American actress. She has appeared in the 2009 film Youth in Revolt as Sheeni Saunders, in the 2011 film Big Mommas: Like Father Like Son as Jasmine Lee and in the 2013 film Carrie as Chris Hargensen. Since 2015, she stars as Angela Moss in the USA Network television drama, Mr. Robot. Portia_Ann_Doubleday ( born June_22_,_1988 ) is an_American_actress .
